allCards.name: Skull Guardian
allCards.description: This monster can only be Ritual Summoned with the Ritual Spell Card, 'Novox's Prayer'. You must also offer monsters whose total Level Stars equal 7 or more as a Tribute from the field or your hand.

allCards.name: Spiral Serpent
allCards.description: When huge whirlpools lay cities asunder, it is the hunger of this sea serpent at work. No one has ever escaped its dreaded Spiral Wave to accurately describe the terror they experienced.

allCards.name: Slot Machine
allCards.description: The machine's ability is said to vary according to its slot results.

allCards.name: The Tricky
allCards.description: You can Special Summon this card (from your hand) by discarding 1 card.

allCards.name: Wattkid
allCards.description: A creature that electrocutes opponents with bolts of lightning.

allCards.name: Yomi Ship
allCards.description: If this card is destroyed by battle and sent to the GY: Destroy the monster that destroyed this card.

allCards.name: Texchanger
allCards.description: Once per turn, when your monster is targeted for an attack: You can negate that attack, then Special Summon 1 Cyberse Normal Monster from your hand, Deck, or GY.

allCards.name: Silver Fang
allCards.description: A snow wolf that's beautiful to the eye, but absolutely vicious in battle.

allCards.name: Marshmallon
allCards.description: Cannot be destroyed by battle. After damage calculation, if this card was attacked, and was face-down at the start of the Damage Step: The attacking player takes 1000 damage.

allCards.name: Dark magician
allCards.description: The ultimate wizard in terms of attack and defense.

allCards.name: Dark Blade
allCards.description: They say he is a dragon-manipulating warrior from the dark world. His attack is tremendous, using his great swords with vicious power.

allCards.name: Haniwa
allCards.description: An earthen figure that protects the tomb of an ancient ruler.

allCards.name: Curtain of the dark ones
allCards.description: A curtain that a spellcaster made, it is said to raise a dark power.

allCards.name: Axe Raider
allCards.description: An axe-wielding monster of tremendous strength and agility.

allCards.name: Battle OX
allCards.description: A monster with tremendous power, it destroys enemies with a swing of its axe.

allCards.name: Bitron
allCards.description: A new species found in electronic space. There's not much information on it.
